thread.title_full: Inish Pharmacy reviewed by M.O'S Cork.

author: M.O'S Cork.
title: M.O'S Cork.
text:
I came across Inish Pharmacy online & my order, which would have cost €66 here in my local pharmacy in Cork, was delivered to my door next morning at a cost of €53.15 including delivery.
Need I say anymore except that I will be recommending them to all my friends. Well done & thank you Inish Pharmacy
